{"tid":144230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<抵制韓貨> 中國抗議薩德  樂天商店卻被一掃而空","createTime":"2017-03-05T09:04:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T02:26:54.000Z","uid":62257,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d6be08ba66de908695598a2827451d107b0baf","tid":144230,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1993629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1993629&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=824f0d35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1993629&h=322cc178\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1993629</a><br />\n2017-03-05  08:29<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國將在南韓部署「戰區高空防禦系統」（THAAD，簡稱薩德），引起中國強烈反彈，同意與南韓國防部換地的樂天集團首當其衝，共青團號召民眾抵制樂天。但中國媒體發現，最近樂天旗下的商店不但沒有銷售低迷，商品還被一掃而空。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpoY9Itg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpoY9Itg.jpg&h=71ac8733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/mar/5/images/bigPic/400_400/php5fDTU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fmar%2F5%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2Fphp5fDTU9.jpg&h=8f973fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據中國《江蘇網》報導，南韓樂天旗下在江蘇港城3家瑪特超市，商店內的銷售異常的好。超市工作人員表示，流量已是平常的好幾倍，營業額不斷攀升，而大多都是使用購物卡消費。<br />\n許多民眾擔心樂天可能倒閉，便出現恐慌性消費，而且幾乎九成已上的消費者使用購物卡結賬，還有人一次就刷了幾萬元人民幣。有顧客表示，購物卡內餘額用完後就不會再去。"},{"pid":"a32ea5a8247c83d6d328ab36dc2f749f67bacfc1","tid":144230,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"見怪不怪。<br />\n口裡說不，身體卻很誠實。"},{"pid":"f7b84bf271c60b59e107229b0afcec0a24afd0e2","tid":144230,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:08:10.000Z","